@jonasschnelli Super nice. Some ideas...

Highlight wallet txes in the mempool and maybe block flyovers, user will be looking for them.

To @gmaxwell's idea about "motion," maybe it could represent the activity that interrelates the three objects shown.   New txes and blocks visually fly from the received-from node to their lists.  A gaggle of txes bunches up and flies into a new block (I gues

@luke-jr: The custom font is about 50% of the UX feeling. If i would go back to Arial or something which is available on OSX/Win/Linux it would really look bad.
The font is totally embedded. No need to install or anything like this.
You have to trust me here. :)
